abstract: The Web turned into a roller coaster ride of speculation over the weekend as a possible prototype of the next generation iPhone made it into the hands of technology bloggers.
snippet: The Web turned into a roller coaster ride of speculation over the weekend as a possible prototype of the next generation iPhone made it into the hands of technology bloggers.
lead_paragraph: Technology bloggers were riveted over the weekend as photos of what might be a yet unannounced next generation iPhone began circulating.

headline.main: Web Buzzing Over Possible New Version of the iPhone
